{"tid":1712251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[下一間一定去科大屠城]科技大學要求警員停止具煽動性言論","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T15:20:59.000Z","uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6281bbd83304537c3ece2ac18bdc557e33ad699f","tid":1712251,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=369649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369649&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7QNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d2e26036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369649&h=f6a71048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=369649</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】香港科技大學發聲明，要求警員停止極不恰當兼具煽動性的言論。<br />\n<br />\n科大指就一名同學離世，有警員提到要「開香檳慶祝」，科大留意到警隊已表示言論極不恰當兼具煽動性。<br />\n<br />\n不過警方表態後，個別警員在周一晚拘捕一名科大學生時，仍繼續作出有關言論，加劇對立局面，科大認為必須停止這種行為。<br />\n<br />\n科大指出另一方面，個別警員於上述情況，作出挑釁性言論，絕非科大學生會在社交媒體網頁鼓吹慶祝警員殉職的理據，認為此類不人道的說話，只會誘發更多暴力行為，絕非文明社會應有的言論，大學對此深表遺憾。"},{"pid":"7371570f64aa1d7d19f04126de4b4071c334176d","tid":1712251,"uid":68226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"我哋已經有policy 一定要出示學生證先可以入校內 <br />\n科大d職員黃到仆街 班黑警連南北閘都未必入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2b528b7bf6095fcf63cd5f3ce0d765ecbbd686","tid":1712251,"uid":300165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6281bbd83304537c3ece2ac18bdc557e33ad699f","tid":1712251,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=369649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369649&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7QNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d2e26036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fne